I have worked in the management and leadership development space for over 30 years and the ability to hold a difficult conversation well is a critical element to successful management and leadership.  However, it is also a life skill, imagine having within you the capability of holding difficult conversations with anyone you encounter? The good news is there is a blue print for success and we will share this an more with you in the module.
